\emph{\unit[20]{min}}.\marginnote[-1em]{The pale blue light is visible
  to all.}

\textbf{Light} enchants one object within \emph{\unit[120]{ft}} for
\emph{\unit[1]{h} + \unit[10]{min/level}} so that it shines faint
light with a \emph{\unit[15]{ft}} radius.\marginnote[-2em]{If you target the
  eyes of a creature, it will go blind for as long as the spell lasts.
  Blind creatures are at -4 to hit. Targets are granted a saving throw
  vs.~spells.}

\textbf{Magic Missile} hits any visible target within
\emph{\unit[150]{ft}} and causes 1d6+1 damage.\marginnote{There is no
  saving throw!} At 5\th level, \emph{three} missiles can be shot at
the same time and they hit different targets. At 10\th level,
\emph{five} missiles can be shot.

\textbf{Read Magic} allows you to decipher magical runes for
\emph{\unit[10]{min}}. This is how to read spell books, scrolls and
magical inscriptions.

\textbf{Sleep} puts \emph{2d8 hit dice} of creatures within
\emph{\unit[240]{ft}} to sleep for \emph{4d4 $\times$ \unit[10]{min}}.
This is a magical slumber.\marginnote{There is no saving throw!} They
need to be slapped in order to wake them before the spell ends. No
creature may have more than 4+1~hit dice. Creatures with less hit dice
are affected first.

